<br>
Things I can say up front:<br>
<br>
1)  Resists are the key.  The higher your FR/CR and MR, the better.<br>
<br>
2)  This isn't about loot.  It's about the challege.<br>
<br>
3)  It takes a long time to do it.  Are there things that can speed it up?  Sure, but they are difficult to do in a dynamically formed raid party.<br>
<br>
4)  It is VERY important for people to listen to those who are running the raid.<br>
<br>
5)  Generally, you want to have tanks level 40 or higher and casters 45 or higher.  Obviously, you want to have an entire raid party of 49 to 52, but it's an unrealistic expectation.  Are there exceptions to those level ranges?  Sure.  It's handed case-by-case, though.<br>
<br>
With those things stated, let the questions roll in.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ulymemarionette.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lyme marionette</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#8E9173>(10/13/00 9:16:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fcouncilofguildsfrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=16.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Plane raid questions:</span><hr size=1> <br>
